description:
A masterful mixer who needs no introduction, TamaOnSen's original pack has arrived!
In addition to super-popular hits like "Uki Yomichi (feat. Ranko, Uten-Kekkoh)" and "Monosugoi Vibes de MARISA ga Monosugoi Rap (MASPA!! Remix)," Sanae Kochiya's VA Kanae Itoh sings the vocals on an original song: "Yururu Toumeido (feat. Sanae Kochiya [CV: Kanae Itoh], Rapbit)"!

This pack contains the following:

■6 songs
・Monosugoi Vibes de MARISA ga Monosugoi Rap (MASPA!! Remix)
・Uki Yomichi (feat. Ranko, Uten-Kekkoh)
・Amanojaku Reverse（feat.ｙｔｒ)
・Warabe Matsuri (feat. AO)
・Tairin no Soul (feat. AO, SBF)
・Yururu Toumeido (feat. Sanae Kochiya [CV: Kanae Itoh], Rapbit)

■6 Challenge Stages
・Lv5 Kappas (Warabe Matsuri (feat. AO))
・Lv6 A Fuss For Two (Uki Yomichi (feat. Ranko, Uten-Kekkoh))
・Lv7 Blue, Yellow, Red...then Green? (Tairin no Soul (feat. AO, SBF))
・Lv8 Gensokyo All Shaken Up
　(Yururu Toumeido (feat. Sanae Kochiya [CV: Kanae Itoh], Rapbit))
・Lv9 Who're You Calling "Weak"?! (Amanojaku Reverse（feat.ｙｔｒ))
・Lv10 An Awesome Spell Bubble and an Awesome Combo
　(Monosugoi Vibes de MARISA ga Monosugoi Rap (MASPA!! Remix))

* Internet connection required for purchase.
* Game must be restarted after songs are purchased in order to use them.
name: TamaOnSen Song Pack
